::Shadow Wing::

She was loosing feeling in her legs. Being in such a cramped 
postition for such a long time was geting to her.  She closed ehr 
eyes and thought about soaring high above the trees with her wings 
stretched out and feeling the cold breeze under her wings.  She then 
opened her eyes and saw a tooth dangerously close to her head.  She 
moved a bit and tried to keep away from the teeth.  She called 
out,"Lunarpine!"  She could feel herself sliding down a little 
towards the cat's throat. She grabbed onto a tooth and held on.  She 
was getting really nervouse.
